      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是Logistics_DeliveryRoute，通过create动作到DRAFT，再用publish到OPEN。那OPEN之后有哪些分支？暂停和关闭都需要吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
