      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，OPEN可以pause变成PAUSED，PAUSED也能resume回到OPEN。另外OPEN有两个终局走向：position filled到FILLED状态，或者close without fill直接到CLOSED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OPEN",
