    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主干画出来：OPEN和PAUSED双向箭头，OPEN分出到FILLED和CLOSED两条线。PAUSED应该也能直接取消吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PAUSED",
        "CLOSED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，PAUSED可以cancel from pause到CLOSED。还有FILLED最终也要close after fill到CLOSED。所有CLOSED最后都要archive到ARCHIVED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PAUSED",
        "CLOSED",
